'''''Myxopyrum'''''<ref name="karinwilke">[https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/429376#page/48/mode/1up Blume, Carl Ludwig von. 1825.  Bijdragen tot de flora van Nederlandsch IndiÃ« 683]</ref> is a plant genus native to [[India]], southern [[China]], [[Southeast Asia]] and [[New Guinea]]. There are at present ({{As of|2014|April|lc=y}}) 4 recognized species:<ref>[http://apps.kew.org/wcsp/namedetail.do?name_id=354447 Kew World Checklist of Selected Plant Families, ''Myxopyrum'']</ref>

*''[[Myxopyrum nervosum]]'' <small>Blume</small><ref name="karinwilke"/> - [[Borneo]], [[Java]], [[Malaysia]], [[Maluku (province)|Maluku]], [[Sulawesi]], [[Sumatra]], [[New Guinea]]
**[[Myxopyrum nervosum subsp. coriaceum|subsp. ''coriaceum'']] <small>(Blume) Kiew</small> - [[Borneo]]
**[[Myxopyrum nervosum subsp. nervosum|subsp. ''nervosum'']]
*''[[Myxopyrum ovatum]]'' <small>A.W.Hill</small> - [[Maluku Islands|Maluku]], the [[Philippines]], [[New Guinea]], [[Bismarck Archipelago]]
*''[[Myxopyrum pierrei]]'' <small>Gagnep. in H.Lecomte</small> - [[Hainan]], [[Vietnam]], [[Cambodia]], [[Thailand]], [[Borneo]]
*''[[Myxopyrum smilacifolium]]'' <small>(Wall.) Blume</small> - [[Hainan]], [[Bangladesh]], [[Cambodia]], [[India]], [[Assam]], [[Laos]], [[Myanmar]], [[Thailand]], [[Vietnam]], [[Andaman & Nicobar Islands]]
**[[Myxopyrum smilacifolium subsp. confertum|subsp. ''confertum'']] <small>(Kerr) P.S.Green</small> - [[Laos]], [[Thailand]], [[Vietnam]]
**[[Myxopyrum smilacifolium subsp. smilacifolium|subsp. ''smilacifolium'']] - [[Hainan]], [[Assam]], [[Bangladesh]], [[India]], [[Andaman & Nicobar Islands]], [[Myanmar]], [[Thailand]], [[Vietnam]]

